name: ReInvenTrip Daily Adventures #002 - Bug in the Hic Et Nunc (Here and Now)
description: I can't help but notice the bug still plagues us hic et nunc (here and now)! Covid Delta or Hen Exploit? You decide. Day 2 of Rediscovering prior versions of myself. Work I created over 20 years ago, explored anew and reinvented for the NFT space on HEN. Based on a digital drawing done in Photoshop with a Wacom tablet in 2001. [Twitter: @AyZe]
